## Base
- **Base URL:** `https://example.com/api/v1`  <!-- TODO -->
- **Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer <token>` / `X-Practicum-Mobile-Token: <token>` <!-- TODO: pick one -->
- **Encoding:** JSON, `application/json`
- **Date format:** ISO8601 (use `JSONDecoder.DateDecodingStrategy.iso8601`)

## Networking baseline
- Use `URLSession.shared.data(for:)` with `async/await`.
- Wrap networking in an `actor NetworkClient`.
- Errors: define `enum NetworkError: LocalizedError` (noConnection, decoding, http(Int), unauthorized, unknown).
- ALWAYS handle: no internet, server error, decoding error.
- Show user-facing errors via dedicated state in ViewModel — NEVER show raw `Error.localizedDescription` in production.

